data.description: Welcome to the coveted Goldcrest Estates, an exclusive 55+ gated community in Nampa. Stay active and social w/ a host of amenities at the clubhouse, which features a fitness room, a library, a billiards area, a game room, and a fully equipped kitchen, dance floor, indoor pool, hot tub, pickleball, horseshoes, communal garden, and RV parking!   Once home, you will be greeted by a split-bedroom design with vaulted ceilings, upgraded lighting, recent interior paint, and updated laminate flooring. The secondary bedrooms now feature plush new carpet, while the laundry room and guest bathroom sport fresh vinyl flooring. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, breakfast bar, pantry, and a spacious dining area.  Outside, this turn-key home provides a fully fenced yard with low-maintenance landscaping and room for your own garden beds and potted plants. Relax on the back patio as you savor the warmth of the eastern sunrise and the cooling shade in the evenings. So much to love at the wonderful community!
